snippet.title: Kick To Hell (Trailer)
snippet.description:
In Kick To Hell you control Jeremiah returning home from work, until after desecrating a ritual, inexplicable things start to happen and something starts to chase you.

Note: All themes and characters covered in this game are from a fictional universe and do not portray reality!

Game link: https://caramelgames.itch.io/kick-to-hell
